          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1705677621669-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1705677621669-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ginger paste</strong>,<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong>,<strong> hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>fish sauce</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>fragrant sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1402.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1402.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1402.-step-5-x700.jpg",
